songs.title: Lock Box
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Uh, I wake up in the morning feel amazing
Hit-Boy
Wake up, huh
G. Ry [?]

[Chorus]
I wake up in the morning, feel amazing, it’s amazing
Getting faded on the daily, run to the cash, it ain’t no waiting
Taking these Percocets, they turn me like pages
I’m getting so high, like I’m going through phases
Yeah, I know these bitches crazy, still wanna have my baby
When she get me started, no I can’t stop
She took my heart and put it in a lock box
How I’m the famous nigga, but I’m fanned out
She the type to make a nigga jaw drop

[Verse 1]
Uh, straight to the floor I mean it
Percocet pop, the opposite of speeding
She came from heaven, opposite of demon
Yeah we got a lot of disagreements
Disagreements got me fiending
She’s unique, her uniqueness got me to the point where I can’t speak
Aw, in love, fallen
She got game, Michael Jordan
She ride me like a horse, Ralph Lauren
She ride me like a whore and I love it
Oh oh scoring
She is everything but boring
And if she ever leaves, I’m forced in enormous torment

[Chorus]
I wake up in the morning, feel amazing, it’s amazing
Getting faded on the daily, run to the cash, it ain’t no waiting
Taking these Percocets, they turn me like pages
I’m getting so high, like I’m going through phases
Yeah, I know these bitches crazy, still wanna have my baby
When she get me started, no I can’t stop
She took my heart and put it in a lock box
How I’m the famous nigga, but I’m fanned out
She the type to make a nigga jaw drop
